 81вҶ’      <div className={styles.drawingHint}>
 82вҶ’        Roof creation is truss-driven. Add a roof-ready truss system first, then create the roof from that truss so the roof outline, shape, pitch family, and support elevation all follow the truss system.
 83вҶ’      </div>
 84вҶ’      {!attachableTrussSystems.length ? (
